Ques : Reverse an Array/String

code:
public static String reverseWord(String str){
    StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder(str);
    int i=0;
    int j= sb.length()-1;
    while(i<j){
        char temp = sb.charAt(i);
        sb.setCharAt(i,sb.charAt(j)); 
        sb.setCharAt(j,temp);
        i++;
        j--;
    }
    return sb.toString();
}

complexity:
time: O(n)
space: O(n)

